艾斯利兄弟因乐队名称商标而告上法庭https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-isley-brothers-headed-to-court-over-band-name-trademark-3488711?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=the-isley-brothers-headed-因品牌名称商标而向法院提起诉讼Anagricel DuranFri, 25 Aug 2023 16:03:17 +0000 Music NewsNewsFunkPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3488711 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/The-Isley-Brothers-posing.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="美国灵魂乐流行乐队艾斯利兄弟（从左至右）O&#39;Kelly Isley Jnr、Ronnie Isley 和 Rudolph Isley，在英国进行巡演。 （标准晚报/盖蒂图片社拍摄）" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/The-Isley-Brothers-posing.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/The-Isley-Brothers-posing-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/The-Isley-Brothers-posing-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/The-Isley-Brothers-posing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/The-Isley-Brothers-posing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/The-Isley-Brothers-posing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>鲁道夫·艾斯利 (Rudolph Isley) 和罗纳德·艾斯利 (Ronald Isley) 兄弟自今年早些时候以来一直就乐队名称所有权问题陷入法律纠纷。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-isley-brothers-headed-to-court-over-band-name-trademark-3488711">艾斯利兄弟 (The Isley Brothers) 因乐队名称商标问题而告上法庭的</a>帖子首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/The-Isley-Brothers-posing.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="美国灵魂乐流行乐队艾斯利兄弟（从左至右）O&#39;Kelly Isley Jnr、Ronnie Isley 和 Rudolph Isley，在英国进行巡演。 （标准晚报/盖蒂图片社拍摄）" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/The-Isley-Brothers-posing.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/The-Isley-Brothers-posing-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/The-Isley-Brothers-posing-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/The-Isley-Brothers-posing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/The-Isley-Brothers-posing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/The-Isley-Brothers-posing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>据透露，<a href="/artists/isley-brothers">艾斯利兄弟</a>将就艾斯利兄弟乐队名称的权利向法庭提起诉讼。</p><p>鲁道夫·艾斯利和罗纳德·艾斯利两兄弟自今年早些时候以来一直就乐队名称的所有权问题陷入法律纠纷。据<a href="https://www.billboard.com/business/legal/isley-brothers-court-battle-over-band-name-legal-rights-1235399882/"><em>Billboard</em></a>报道，在 8 月 23 日星期三做出的裁决中，托马斯·M·德金法官拒绝驳回鲁道夫对罗纳德的诉讼。</p><p>在诉讼中，鲁道夫指控他的兄弟罗纳德不当试图以“艾斯利兄弟”的名字注册个人商标。鲁道夫认为他们应该平等地拥有一半的权利。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/CtP78whvjgG/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stro