·柯蒂斯和海莉·贝内特。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/kevin-hart-in-wheelchair-after-tearing-abdomen-in-race-with-ex-nfl-player-3488714">凯文·哈特 (Kevin Hart) 在与前 NFL 球员比赛中腹部撕裂后坐在轮椅上的</a>帖子首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
 《博德之门 3》开启了“短暂的国王之夏”，补丁说明对 Steam 来说太大了https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/baldurs-gate-3-kicks-off-short-king-summer-with-patch-notes-too-big-for-steam-3488636?utm_source= rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=baldurs-gate-3-kicks-off-short-king-summer-with-patch-notes-too-big-for-steamImogen Donovan Fri, 25 Aug 2023 15:56:01 +0000 Gaming NewsNewsPC https://www.nme.com/?p=3488636 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/baldurs-gate-3-short-king-summer-2.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/baldurs-gate-3-short-king-summer-2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/baldurs-gate-3-short-king-summer-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/baldurs-gate-3-short-king-summer-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/baldurs-gate-3-short-king-summer-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/baldurs-gate-3-short-king-summer-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/baldurs-gate-3-short-king-summer-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>大风现在不像以前那么浪漫了</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/baldurs-gate-3-kicks-off-short-king-summer-with-patch-notes-too-big-for-steam-3488636">《博德之门 3》的帖子拉开了“短暂的国王之夏”的序幕，其补丁说明对 Steam 来说太大，</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/baldurs-gate-3-short-king-summer-2.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/baldurs-gate-3-short-king-summer-2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/baldurs-gate-3-short-king-summer-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/baldurs-gate-3-short-king-summer-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/baldurs-gate-3-short-king-summer-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/baldurs-gate-3-short-king-summer-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/baldurs-gate-3-short-king-summer-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/games/baldurs-gate-iii"><em>《博德之门 3》</em></a>的第一个补丁解决了流行的<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/dungeons-dragons"><em>《龙与地下城》</em></a>游戏中的 1,000 多个问题，其中包括矮个子角色无法亲吻他们的浪漫同伴的问题。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/game-reviews/baldurs-gate-3-review-3481761">《博德之门 3》评论：必玩奇幻游戏大获好评</a></strong></li></ul><p>“今天我们发布了<em>《博德之门 3》</em>的第一个主要补丁，解决了 1000 多个错误、平衡、流程问题等等，”社区经理 Salo 在<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/larian-studios">Larian Studios</a>官方论坛上 <a href="https://forums.larian.com/ubbthreads.php?ubb=showflat&amp;Number=886485&amp;#Post886485">发帖</a>说。</p><p>虽然<a href="https://store.steampowered.com/news/app/1086940/view/3669924544085723479">更新也已共享</a>到<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/steam">Steam</a> ，但完整的补丁说明可以在开发者自己的网站上找到，因为它超出了 Steam 对单个帖子的字符数限制。</p><p>诸如漂浮物品、无限下落循环、第三幕中陷入停滞的暗影之心浪漫以及当矮人、侏儒和半身人等矮个角色想要亲吻他们的伴侣时意外的不雅定位等错误都已得到纠正。拉里安工作室得意地说，团队在最后一部作品中“带回了短暂的国王夏天”。 </p><figure id="attachment_3488727" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3488727" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3488727" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/baldurs-gate-3-short-king-summer-1.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/baldurs-gate-3-short-king-summer-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/baldurs-gate-3-short-king-summer-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/baldurs-gate-3-short-king-summer-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/baldurs-gate-3-short-king-summer-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/baldurs-gate-3-short-king-summer-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/baldurs-gate-3-short-king-summer-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3488727" class="wp-caption-text"> 《博德之门 3》图片来源：Larian Studios</figcaption></figure><p>此外，该补丁“让你在选择某些对话选项时与盖尔开始一段浪漫关系变得更加明确”，并且“在盖尔的咒语教学场景中，你现在可以选择与盖尔一起描绘介于两者之间的未来”亲吻他并踢他的头”。</p><p>由于这些不一致，盖尔被解释为一个无可救药的浪漫主义者，玩家们惊讶地发现他突然向他们的角色发出最后通牒，要求选择他或玩家真正喜爱的同伴。这些修复应该会让他更受球迷欢迎。</p><p>同样，整个补丁说明都可以在 Larian Studios 的论坛上找到，但它们确实包含故事剧透，所以那些还没有完成游戏的人应该意识到这一点。</p><p>其他消息称， <em>《博德之门 3》</em>将于今年年底前<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/baldurs-gate-3-xbox-series-x-and-xbox-series-s-versions-wont-share-the-same-features-3488513">推出 Xbox 版</a>，但该游戏的<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/xbox-series-x">Xbox Series X</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/xbox-series-s">Xbox Series S</a>版本将不会共享相同的功能。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/baldurs-gate-3-kicks-off-short-king-summer-with-patch-notes-too-big-for-steam-3488636">《博德之门 3》的帖子拉开了“短暂的国王之夏”的序幕，其补丁说明对 Steam 来说太大，</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
卡洛斯·桑塔纳为跨性别群体的“麻木不仁的评论”道歉https://www.nme.com/news/music/carlos-santana-apologises-for-insensitive-comments-about-transgender-community-3488709?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=carlos-santana-apologises-for-insensitive-关于跨性别者社区的评论Hollie GeraghtyFri, 25 Aug 2023 15:54:38 +0000 Music NewsNewsBluesJazzRockhttps://www.nme.com/?p=3488709 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/carlos-santana-trans-apology.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/carlos-santana-trans-apology.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/carlos-santana-trans-apology-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/carlos-santana-trans-apology-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/carlos-santana-trans-apology-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/carlos-santana-trans-apology-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/carlos-santana-trans-apology-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这位吉他手此前曾在台上提出“女人就是女人，男人就是男人”</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/carlos-santana-apologises-for-insensitive-comments-about-transgender-community-3488709">卡洛斯·桑塔纳 (Carlos Santana) 为跨性别群体的“麻木不仁的评论”道歉的帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/carlos-santana-trans-apology.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/carlos-santana-trans-apology.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/carlos-santana-trans-apology-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/carlos-santana-trans-apology-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2